{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>You feel an inexplicable power call to you, find the source.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/CF_Trailer-middle.gif?t=1734917058\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>Chaotic roguelike action</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each run is different from the last, featuring <strong>random-gen</strong> levels, <strong>artifacts</strong>, and <strong>pseudo-random</strong> weapons. Travel through four biomes, fight relentless enemies and bosses who strategically fight to <strong>destroy you</strong>. Gather weapons and artifacts that\u00a0<strong>burn, bleed, freeze,</strong> and<strong> slow</strong>\u00a0enemies to get the upper hand.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Artifacts</strong>\u00a0are <i>stackable</i> upgrades that give you permanent bonuses for your run. Gather enough of them and snowball your power. With good synergies between your character, guns, and artifacts, you <i>might</i> stand a chance.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">-Synergize-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/icicle.gif?t=1734917058\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Upgrade</i></strong> your run with unique, run-defining artifacts. Experiment to find possibly game-breaking synergies. These artifacts are <strong>stackable</strong> and essential if you want to survive. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Look out for guns that work well with the artifacts you pick up. <i>For example,</i> the artifact <strong>&quot;Icicle&quot;</strong> makes every bullet shatter into shards of ice, which works well with the large bullet count from <strong>shotguns</strong>.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">-Arm Yourself-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/gun-stats-short.gif?t=1734917058\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Every</strong> weapon you find will have <strong>random</strong> stats. The higher the rarity, the more the stats will change. Many artifacts change the properties of weapons.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tight</strong>\u00a0gameplay and chaotic action.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Randomly generated</strong> levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Synergistic</strong> item/gun/character combos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>45</strong> <strong>artifacts</strong> with unique benefits/drawbacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>26</strong> weapons, <strong>endless</strong> weapon variety.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>6</strong>\u00a0different enemy modifiers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Controller support.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optional auto-aim (default: TAB)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Starting Off Strong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2616890/0171370d6389517d1a734597726d69900f8566fb.jpg"},{"name":"You Can't See Me","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2616890/bbd4e0ba8527b3569dabfe97504c971889e7784c.jpg"},{"name":"My Soldiers Rage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2616890/dfe8bbbcb6fcd5182f180d072ce49139232dbb0b.jpg"},{"name":"One Down","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2616890/0d15eaf576110c329056558d947d68e2181386bb.jpg"},{"name":"Snowed In","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2616890/c98084005d82df37a1e7106638052aff7f4a1a62.jpg"},{"name":"Don't Blink","pa